{"text": "I have heard that on one occasion the Blessed One was staying near Rajagaha on Vulture's Peak Mountain, in the Boar's Cave. Then LongNails the wanderer [1] went to the Blessed One and, on arrival, exchanged courteous greetings with him. After an exchange of friendly greetings & courtesies, he stood to one side. As he was standing there, he said to the Blessed One, \"Master Gotama, I am of the view, of the opinion, that 'All is not pleasing to me.'\"", "entities": [["PERSON", "Blessed One"], ["GPE", "Rajagaha"], ["LOC", "Vulture's Peak Mountain"], ["LOC", "Boar's Cave"], ["PERSON", "LongNails"], ["PERSON", "Master Gotama"]]}
