{"text": "I have heard that on one occasion the Blessed One was staying near Savatthi at Jeta's Grove, Anathapindika 's monastery. Now at that time a certain householder's dear & beloved little son, his only child, had died. Because of his death, the father had no desire to work or to eat. He kept going to the cemetery and crying out, \"Where have you gone, my only little child? Where have you gone, my only little child?\"", "entities": [["PERSON", "Blessed One"], ["GPE", "Savatthi"], ["LOC", "Jeta's Grove"], ["LOC", "Anathapindika's monastery"]]}
