{"text": "Now at that time, young Sigala , a householder's son, rising early in the morning, departing from Rajagaha, with wet clothes and wet hair, worshipped with joined hands the various quarters — the East, the South, the West, the North, the Nadir, and the Zenith.", "entities": [["GPE", "Rajagaha"]]}
