{"text": "Then Subha the student, Todeyya's son , went to the Blessed One and, on arrival, exchanged courteous greetings with him. After an exchange of friendly greetings & courtesies, he sat to one side. As he was sitting there, he said to the Blessed One: \"Master Gotama, what is the reason, what is the cause, why baseness & excellence are seen among human beings, among the human race? For short-lived & long-lived people are to be seen, sickly & healthy, ugly & beautiful, uninfluential & influential, poor & rich, low-born & high-born, stupid & discerning people are to be seen. So what is the reason, what is the cause, why baseness & excellence are seen among human beings, among the human race?\"", "entities": [["PERSON", "Subha"], ["PERSON", "Todeyya's"], ["PERSON", "Blessed One"], ["PERSON", "Master Gotama"]]}
