{"text": "When this was said, one of the wanderers said to Vajjiya Mahita the householder, \"Now wait a minute, householder. This contemplative Gotama whom you praise is a nihilist, one who doesn't declare anything.\"", "entities": [["PERSON", "Gotama"]]}
