{"text": "When this was said, Ven. Mahā Kaccāyana said to Soṇa Koṭikaṇṇa, \"It's hard, Soṇa, the life-long, one-meal-a-day, sleeping-alone holy life. Please, right there as you are a householder, devote yourself to the message of the Awakened Ones and to the proper-time [i.e., uposatha day], one-meal-a-day, sleeping-alone holy life.\" And so Soṇa Koṭikaṇṇa's idea of going-forth subsided.", "entities": [["PERSON", "Awakened Ones"]]}
